@startuml
actor "Sinh viên" as Student
participant "AccountManagement\n(Frontend)" as FE
participant "UserController" as UC
participant "UserService" as US
participant "UserRepository" as UR
database "Database" as DB

== Xem Profile ==
Student -> FE: Truy cập trang cá nhân
FE -> UC: GET /api/users/profile
activate UC

UC -> US: getProfile()
activate US
US -> UR: findById(userId)
activate UR
UR -> DB: SELECT * FROM users WHERE id = ?
DB --> UR: User Entity
deactivate UR

US -> US: Map User to ProfileResponse
US --> UC: ProfileResponse
deactivate US

UC --> FE: 200 OK
deactivate UC
FE -> Student: Hiển thị thông tin cá nhân

== Cập nhật Profile ==
Student -> FE: Thay đổi thông tin & Lưu
FE -> FE: Validate form
FE -> UC: PUT /api/users/profile (UpdateProfileRequest)
activate UC

UC -> US: updateProfile(request)
activate US

US -> UR: findById(userId)
activate UR
UR --> US: User Entity
deactivate UR

US -> US: Update fields (name, phone, etc.)
US -> UR: save(user)
activate UR
UR -> DB: UPDATE users SET ...
DB --> UR: Updated Entity
deactivate UR

US --> UC: Updated Profile
deactivate US

UC --> FE: 200 OK
deactivate UC

FE --> Student: Thông báo "Cập nhật thành công"
@enduml